### Get all items for a shopping list
GET http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-lists/1/items

###

### Create shopping list item (make sure shopping list 1, category 1, and user 1 exist)
POST http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-list-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shoppingListId": 1,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Apples",
  "quantity": "6",
  "addedBy": 1,
  "order": 1
}

###

### Create another item
POST http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-list-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shoppingListId": 1,
  "categoryId": 2,
  "name": "Milk",
  "quantity": "2 liters",
  "addedBy": 1,
  "order": 2
}

###

### Get item by ID
GET http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-list-items/1

###

### Update item (mark as checked)
PUT http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-list-items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Apples",
  "quantity": "6",
  "isChecked": true,
  "order": 1
}

###

### Delete item
DELETE http://localhost:5162/api/shopping-list-items/1
